{"tid":2215771,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"胡雅文判三名沙田714手足 分別三年四個月至四年監禁","createTime":"2020-09-24T08:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T09:21:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"29d162ed25c406093dd9b133ad5dca5f88735879","tid":2215771,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"#區域法院第廿八庭<br />\n#胡雅文法官<br />\n#判刑<br />\n#0714沙田<br />\n<br />\n梁 (24) 已還押30天<br />\n龔 (51) 已還押20天<br />\n李 (17) 已還押20天<br />\n<br />\n兩項暴動罪<br />\n<br />\n控罪詳情：2019年7月14日在沙田新城市廣場，首被告以及第2被告各參與2次暴動，而第3被告參與1次暴動<br />\n<br />\n答辯詳情<br />\n<br />\n📌判刑理由：<br />\n（詳情後補）<br />\n<br />\n速報：<br />\n梁 合共判處4年監禁<br />\n龔 合共判處4年監禁<br />\n李 判處3年又4個月監禁"},{"pid":"2e17faa27754b3016c8699b3f7e5b43380e1b78d","tid":2215771,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:05:12.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9780&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=d66fe27f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9780</a>"},{"pid":"af509aabbd9bc7ba435623f9ff889f4f5ed8bec1","tid":2215771,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:05:46.000Z","msg":"送車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05936ad1697faa1cfeae9573d60cdbd9ba3f766","tid":2215771,"uid":108757,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T08:07:01.000Z","msg":"死肥閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22189bc2cd001f7d70fdaae619b198ceec